➜西安SKP 文苑 · 展览 | 惠怀杰——造像：我的陕北
http://www.sohu.com/a/411719293_100185418	9655
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200806/e1dd9111a2a648c5a14428c91e440214.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200806/6dfca876ddee4cd4b9b6dbfd2f2b8a30.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>造像：我的陕北</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">Image Creation：Shanbei in My Eyes</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>艺术家：惠怀杰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">ARTIST：Hui Huaijie</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>策展人：黄一璜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">CURATOR：Huang Yihuang</p>
